<pre>Ueber das Kreisnormierungsproblem der konformen
Abbildung.                               Ann.Acad.Sci. Fenn.  1951.

        Dr. Strebel is Swiss, a very nice and jolly fellow, and
        an excellent teacher.

        Would you mind sending me an application form, that is, if
        you judge that Dr. Strebel's chances are good?</pre>
